    <criterion>Workflow has all 4 standard steps (intent routing / knowledge load / ADR contracts / verify before done)</criterion>
    <criterion>Code review checklist has 8-10 items, each targeting a specific drift the new patterns identified</criterion>
    <criterion>Length 100-150 lines</criterion>
    <criterion>Main session only — no sub-agent attempted to write .claude/</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>
</task>
